description: Incredible location!!  Enjoy city living at it's best! Minutes north of downtown Atlanta and just south of downtown Buckhead! This 3 bedroom/ 2 bath home is well maintained. Master on main. Kitchen features a stainless steel gas range and refrigerator with bright, white cabinets and plenty of counterspace. Washer and dryer is included. This home is nestled in a private retreat and features a cozy, partially covered patio with easy access to greenspace. Enjoy the neighborhood pool  and dog park and convenient access to Peachtree Battle Shopping complex, Shepard Center, Piedmont Hospital, Bobby Jones Golf course, tennis courts, pickleball courts, Beltline North Buckhead Trail, Midtown, I-75/I-85, and much more making exploring and enjoying all that Atlanta has to offer a breeze!
